\family typewriter
MOOSAsyncCommClient
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The key class is 
\family typewriter
MOOS::MOOSAsyncCommClient 
\family default
which is a derivate of the tried and test 
\family typewriter
CMOOSCommClient.
 
\family default
Its interface is identical
\family typewriter
 
\family default
